Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/michal-au/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/.gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Install jedi in case you haven't yet:

     pip install jedi

Update NERDTree with a "custom" grep-script:

    cp grep_menuitem.vim bundle/nerdtree/nerdtree_plugin/
